## ğŸ“ Usage

```python
from txtemo import predict

print(predict("I love this AI model!"))  
# ('Positive ğŸ˜ƒ', 0.92)

print(predict("This is the worst thing ever."))  
# ('Negative ğŸ˜¡', 0.89)

print(predict("Pranesh"))  
# ('Neutral ğŸ˜', 0.75)
```

